junit.framework.Test
public class JtsSnapTest
extends junit.framework.TestCase

In these tests we are trying to probe the use of snapping and precision reduction in JTS operations, to avoid undesired effects (for example spureus lines in dissolve) and to allow clustering tolerance in topologies.

Author:
azabala
